# ========================================
# NOTES
# ========================================
# 
# 1. Get SUPABASE_URL and keys from: 
#    Supabase Dashboard > Settings > API
#
# 2. Get OPENAI_API_KEY from:
#    https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#
# 3. VITE_API_URL should be your Vercel deployment URL
#    Example: https://codeforge-ai.vercel.app
#
# 4. All VITE_ variables are for frontend (exposed to browser)
#    Never put sensitive keys in VITE_ variables!
#
# 5. In Vercel Dashboard, set variables for:
#    - Production (all environments)
#    - Preview (for testing)
#    - Development (for local development)
